The paper discusses the use of machine learning and data analysis techniques for the histological assessment of human tissue, which falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). The paper also mentions the use of survival probability estimation, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.IR, and cs.DL.
